They wanna give you

25:10.301 --> 25:13.178
five for the first, seven for the second.

25:13.262 --> 25:15.013
God willing, if there is a third,

25:15.097 --> 25:17.849
they want to give you 12. Boom!

25:17.933 --> 25:20.894
