25:30.654 --> 25:33.823
Vince, you wanna buy that house?
Do this movie.

25:37.244 --> 25:38.369
All right.

25:41.582 --> 25:43.166
Can you get me suit approval?

25:43.250 --> 25:44.751
You can wear tube socks and a yarmulka!

25:51.800 --> 25:53.343
All right, fuck it. Lock it down.

25:53.427 --> 25:55.178
That's what I'm talking about!

25:55.262 --> 25:56.512
Nice working, baby!

25:56.597 --> 25:58.556
Hey, you know, Aquaman's got a brother.

25:58.641 --> 26:00.391
I'm just saying.

26:00.476 --> 26:02.018
